<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 15:13:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登欢迎肯尼亚鲁托入主白宫并做出投资和承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-welcomes-kenyas-ruto-white-house-with-investments-promises-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周四欢迎肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托到白宫进行国事访问，旨在深化与因乌克兰和加沙战争而被边缘化的非洲国家的关系，并宣布了一系列协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-welcomes-kenyas-ruto-white-house-with-investments-promises-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国阿里巴巴将通过发行可转换票据筹集 45 亿美元资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-raise-45-bln-through-convertible-notes-offering-2024-05-23/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周四表示，将出售 45 亿美元的可转换优先票据，并计划用部分收益回购美国存托股票。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-raise-45-bln-through-convertible-notes-offering-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>宫一专注，水手队瞄准亚洲冠军联赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/miyaichi-focused-marinos-set-sights-asian-champions-league-crown-2024-05-23/</link><description>横滨水手队边锋宫市亮相信日本队能够在周六的亚洲冠军联赛决赛第二回合中保持专注，击败东道主艾因队，夺得洲际冠军。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/miyaichi-focused-marinos-set-sights-asian-champions-league-crown-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>尽管欧盟关税威胁，中国汽车制造商蔚来汽车在阿姆斯特丹开业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-carmaker-nio-unfazed-by-european-tariff-uncertainties-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车创始人李斌周四表示，尽管欧盟是否会对中国电动汽车征收关税存在不确定性，但该公司仍计划继续在欧洲扩张。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-carmaker-nio-unfazed-by-european-tariff-uncertainties-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，谷歌与富士康合作在印度生产 Pixel 手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-ties-up-with-foxconn-make-pixel-phones-india-sources-say-2024-05-23/</link><description>两位直接知情人士周四表示，Alphabet 旗下的谷歌正计划在印度南部泰米尔纳德邦生产 Pixel 智能手机，并已与台湾富士康建立合作关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-ties-up-with-foxconn-make-pixel-phones-india-sources-say-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>大型投资者向新兴市场注入资金，掩盖了新兴市场的资金外流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/bigger-investors-pouring-money-into-emerging-markets-belie-em-outflows-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国银行一位资深经济学家告诉路透社，大资金投资者开始在新兴市场投入更多现金，因为他们追逐回报，这可能是他们配置资金方式的结构性转变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:54:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/bigger-investors-pouring-money-into-emerging-markets-belie-em-outflows-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：欧洲汽车制造商需要时间而不是关税来抵御中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-automakers-need-time-not-tariffs-fend-off-china-competition-2024-05-23/</link><description>行业高管在路透社的一次活动中表示，欧洲汽车巨头不会有太多时间重组其业务和产品线以与崛起的中国汽车制造商竞争，而且更严格的关税对维持现状无济于事。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-automakers-need-time-not-tariffs-fend-off-china-competition-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>起亚摆脱电动汽车需求放缓的影响推出紧凑型电动SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kia-shrugs-off-slowing-ev-demand-launch-compact-electric-suv-2024-05-23/</link><description>起亚公司周四推出了该公司首款基于其专用电动汽车平台打造的紧凑型电动运动型多功能车，并相信即使全球电动汽车市场势头停滞，它也能通过有竞争力的价格赢得买家。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kia-shrugs-off-slowing-ev-demand-launch-compact-electric-suv-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达在美联储、台湾和英国民意调查紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于手机销量强劲，第一季度超出预期，小米将电动汽车目标提高至 12 万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-reports-27-rise-q1-revenue-strong-smartphone-sales-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国小米表示，今年的目标是交付 12 万辆电动汽车 (EV)，高于最初的 10 万辆目标，并将实施双班制生产，以满足日益增长的电动汽车需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-reports-27-rise-q1-revenue-strong-smartphone-sales-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构表示，中国推动公司股息应该吸引投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-push-company-dividends-should-attract-investment-says-regulator-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国一位高级监管机构周四表示，鼓励企业支付更多股息的政府政策应该会让中国股市对海外投资者更具吸引力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-push-company-dividends-should-attract-investment-says-regulator-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>泰国医院称新加坡航空航班上的20人仍在重症监护室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-hospital-says-20-people-singapore-airlines-flight-remain-intensive-care-2024-05-23/</link><description>一名医院官员周四表示，周二新加坡航空一架航班遭遇严重湍流并紧急迫降曼谷，机上的 20 名乘客仍在重症监护室接受治疗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-hospital-says-20-people-singapore-airlines-flight-remain-intensive-care-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国通过模拟攻击向台湾新总统发出严厉警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/with-mock-attacks-china-sends-honed-warning-taiwans-new-president-2024-05-23/</link><description>北京发起了为期两天的惩罚演习，以抗议台湾新就任总统赖清德的分裂本能，这是发出了精心设计的警告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/with-mock-attacks-china-sends-honed-warning-taiwans-new-president-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>万科获批28亿美元境内银团贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-granted-28-bln-onshore-syndicated-loan-facility-2024-05-23/</link><description>现金短缺的大型房地产开发商万科周四表示，已获得 200 亿元人民币（合 27.6 亿美元）的银团贷款融资，并将继续推进其他融资以增加流动性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-granted-28-bln-onshore-syndicated-loan-facility-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席财务官：具体讨论印度汽车合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-cfo-concrete-discussions-over-car-partnerships-india-2024-05-23/</link><description>大众汽车公司财务主管周四表示，该公司正在就在印度进行乘用车生产合作进行具体谈判，并补充说，在仍然存在“明显”机会的市场上赚钱很困难。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:20:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-cfo-concrete-discussions-over-car-partnerships-india-2024-05-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>